te|[[Vladimer Gegeshidze]]|GEO|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 5\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[M\u00e9lonin Noumonvi]]|FRA|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 7\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Pablo Shorey]]|CUB|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n|8\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Vasyl Rachyba]]|UKR|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 9\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Chad Gable|Chas Betts]]|USA|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 10\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Amer Hrustanovi\u0107]]|AUT|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n|11\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Saman Tahmasebi]]|AZE|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 12\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Alim Selimau]]|BLR|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 13\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Habibollah Akhlaghi]]|IRI|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 14\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Nenad \u017dugaj]]|CRO|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n|15\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Rami Hietaniemi]]|FIN|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 15\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Nazmi Avluca]]|TUR|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n|15\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Haykel Achouri]]|TUN|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 18\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Lee Se-yeol]]|KOR|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n|18\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Hristo Marinov]]|BUL|2012 Summer}}\n|-\n| 20\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagIOCathlete|[[Keitani Graham]]|FSM|2012 Summer}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20150924012958/http://www.fila-official.com/images/FILA/resultats/2012/results_08_londres.pdf Page 75]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Wrestling at the 2012 Summer Olympics - Men's Greco-Roman 84 kg}}\n[[Category:Wrestling at the 2012 Summer Olympics]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Men's Greco-Roman 84 kg\n|games = 2012 Summer \n|image = Medalists at the Men's 84 kg Greco Roman Wrestling.jpg\n|image_size = 150px\n|caption =\n|venue = [[ExCeL Exhibition Centre]]\n|date = 6 August\n|competitors = 20\n|nations = 20\n|gold        = [[Alan Khugayev]]\n|goldNOC     =RUS\n|silver      = [[Karam Gaber]]\n|silverNOC   =EGY\n|bronze      = [[Daniyal Gadzhiyev]]\n|bronzeNOC   =KAZ\n|bronze2     = [[Damian Janikowski]]\n|bronzeNOC2  =POL\n|prev = [[Wrestling at the 2008 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 84 kg|2008]]\n|next = [[Wrestling at the 2016 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's Greco-Roman 85 kg|2016]]\n}}\n\n{{WrestlingAt2012SummerOlympics}}\n'''Men's Greco-Roman 84&nbsp;kg''' competition at the [[2012 Summer Olympics]] in [[London]], [[United Kingdom]], took place on 6 August at [[ExCeL London]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.london2012.com/wrestling/event/men-greco-roman-84kg/index.html|title=Men's 84kg Greco-Roman|work=london2012.com|accessdate=18 August 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120823100819/http://www.london2012.com/wrestling/event/men-greco-roman-84kg/index.html#|archive-date=2012-08-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>\nThis [[Greco-Roman wrestling]] competition consists of a single-elimination tournament, with a [[repechage]] used to determine the winner of two bronze medals. The two finalists face off for gold and silver medals. Each wrestler who loses to one of the two finalists moves into the repechage, culminating in a pair of bronze medal matches featuring the semifinal losers each facing the remaining repechage opponent from their half of the bracket.\n\nEach bout consists of up to three rounds, lasting two minutes apiece. The wrestler who scores more points in each round is the winner of that rounds; the bout ends when one wrestler has won two rounds (and thus the match).\n\n==Schedule==\n<small>All times are [[British Summer Time]] ([[UTC+01:00]])</small>\n{|class = \"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! width=150|Date\n! width=50|Time\n! width=150|Event\n|-\n| rowspan=3| 6 August 2012 || 13:00 || Qualification rounds\n|-\n| 17:45 || Repechage\n|-\n| 18:30 || bgcolor=ffffcc|Finals\n|}\n\n==Results==\n;Legend\n*'''F''' \u2014 Won by [[Pin (amateur wrestling)|fall]]\n\n===Final===\n{{2TeamBracket-Tennis3\n| seeds = no\n| RD1=Final\n| nowrap = no\n\n| team-width=205\n| 